  "detailed_description": "<h1>New Game!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/5090db98d4dc891961a3a45574a0c54c.avif?t=1771997724\" width=462 height=174 /></span><br>Please scroll down to MORE FROM RENKA!</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A young female streamer, once the victim of a serial killer, is now reborn as an AI.<br>Your task is to manage her work while uncovering the truth.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/789209c46c05b142231d3bca2c23eae1.webp?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By managing the \"Data Collection\", you can make her grow on the Internet.<br>Different Data Collection has a different effect, by appropriately combining various Data Collections to get the best out of her.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/4048f22c2cca58d307ad03454e62e342.avif?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, personal ability isn't the only necessity in the Internet world. \"Inspiration\" is another crucial factor for making videos that draw people's attention.<br>By collecting different Data Collections to incite more inspiration - creating the ideal streamer.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/ac56ccfe4cce756ab6c5349d84536f87.avif?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Except for the world of the Internet, you can go ahead and ask her out, and have some fun in the real world.<br>People that you meet and things that happen can both inspire you.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/3deba21448492db7f8b198160db611cb.avif?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After you've done all this, you will see rapidly increasing love and numbers.<br>However, is that all she needs? </p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/95738fab09040f2dfa8f6bc7307ebaa2.avif?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At least, fortunately, the story is told by you.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/3f97b1963817a0c86788e3c568392bc3.poster.avif?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/3f97b1963817a0c86788e3c568392bc3.webm?t=1771997724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/3f97b1963817a0c86788e3c568392bc3.mp4?t=1771997724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A young female streamer, once the victim of a serial killer, is now reborn as an AI.<br>Your task is to manage her work while uncovering the truth.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/789209c46c05b142231d3bca2c23eae1.webp?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=60 /></span><br><br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >By managing the \"Data Collection\", you can make her grow on the Internet.<br>Different Data Collection has a different effect, by appropriately combining various Data Collections to get the best out of her.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/4048f22c2cca58d307ad03454e62e342.avif?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Of course, personal ability isn't the only necessity in the Internet world. \"Inspiration\" is another crucial factor for making videos that draw people's attention.<br>By collecting different Data Collections to incite more inspiration - creating the ideal streamer.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/ac56ccfe4cce756ab6c5349d84536f87.avif?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Except for the world of the Internet, you can go ahead and ask her out, and have some fun in the real world.<br>People that you meet and things that happen can both inspire you.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/3deba21448492db7f8b198160db611cb.avif?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >After you've done all this, you will see rapidly increasing love and numbers.<br>However, is that all she needs? </p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/95738fab09040f2dfa8f6bc7307ebaa2.avif?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=240 /></span><br><br><br><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At least, fortunately, the story is told by you.</p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/3f97b1963817a0c86788e3c568392bc3.poster.avif?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/3f97b1963817a0c86788e3c568392bc3.webm?t=1771997724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/3f97b1963817a0c86788e3c568392bc3.mp4?t=1771997724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
